song_lyrics: Tarsat hain more nain, daras hit...
Jāgo kamalnain kamalāvar, bhor bhayo gaī rain;
Mukh pankaj dekhe binā mohe, parat nahi pal chain...  1
Darsan deho Dayānidhi mādho, Shyām sundar sukhḍain;
Premānand kahe vadan kamal par, vāru koṭik main...  2
title: Tarsat hain more nain daras hit
